source.name: Total official flows (official development assistance plus other official flows) to the agriculture sector
source.additionalInfo:
Definition: 
 
Gross disbursements of total ODA and other official flows from all donors to the agriculture sector. 
 
Comments and limitations: 
 
Data in the Creditor Reporting System are available from 1973.  However, the data coverage is 
considered complete since 1995 for commitments at an activity level and 2002 for disbursements. 
 

Data Availability 

 
Description: 
 
On a recipient basis for all developing countries eligible for ODA. 
 
Time series: 
 
Data available since 1973 on an annual (calendar) basis
